OL,3,CParents urged to protect babies from
OL,4,Cwhooping cough
OL,6,FThe UK Health Security Agency says
OL,7,F1,468 cases of whooping cough were
OL,8,Fconfirmed in England between January
OL,9,Fand February 2024. Since then, medical
OL,10,Fprofessionals have reported thousands
OL,11,Fmore suspected cases.
OL,13,FIt comes after a steady decline in the
OL,14,Fuptake of all childhood vaccinations
OL,15,Foffered through the routine NHS
OL,16,Fprogramme in England.
